Hi yifeif,
unicode size is 4 on python 2.7 and `None` with python3.

If I use the URL to install, the installation terminates successfully, but I can't import tensorflow:

    ImportError: /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libc.so.6: version `GLIBC_2.16' not found (required by /home/travis/virtualenv/python2.7.9/lib/python2.7/site-packages/tensorflow/python/_pywrap_tensorflow.so)
